    <title>高质量地从ico转为svg</title>
    <link href="https://thun888.xyz/2021/05/03/%E9%AB%98%E8%B4%A8%E9%87%8F%E5%9C%B0%E4%BB%8Eico%E8%BD%AC%E4%B8%BAsvg/"/>
    <id>https://thun888.xyz/2021/05/03/%E9%AB%98%E8%B4%A8%E9%87%8F%E5%9C%B0%E4%BB%8Eico%E8%BD%AC%E4%B8%BAsvg/</id>
    <published>2021-05-03T11:19:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-07-09T12:08:09.565Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h5 id="效果图"><a href="#效果图" class="headerlink" title="效果图"></a>效果图</h5><p>先上个效果图（上原下后）</p><p><img src="https://thun888.xyz/favicon.ico" alt="favicon.ico (128×128) (thun888.xyz)"></p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/thun888/tuku@master/img/favicon_1.svg" alt="favicon_1" style="zoom:300%;" /><h5 id="How"><a href="#How" class="headerlink" title="How"></a>How</h5><p>先下载&amp;安装<a href="https://share.thun888.xyz/%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6/CorelDRAW_X4_SP2_%E7%B2%BE%E7%AE%80%E5%A2%9E%E5%BC%BA%E7%89%88.exe">CorelDRAW</a></p><p>把你可爱的ico拉到浏览器里放到最大</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/thun888/tuku@master/img/image-20210504155034662.png" alt="image-20210504155034662"></p><p>贴着边缘截张图</p><div class="tag-plugin note"><div class="title"><strong>like this</strong></div><div class="body"><div class="tag-plugin image"><div class="image-bg"><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/thun888/tuku@master/img/20210504155240.png"/></div></div></div></div><p>选择 文件—导入—（刚刚截的图）</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/thun888/tuku@master/img/20210504155534.png"></p><p>放置在画纸后</p><p>右键—轮廓描慕—高质量图像（也可以选其他的）</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/thun888/tuku@master/img/20210504155749.png"></p><p>在这里你可以改变三个参数实现不同的效果</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/thun888/tuku@master/img/dg4df56hde4568.png"></p><p>点击确定后就能得到2个图像（原来的位图和生成的矢量图）</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/thun888/tuku@master/img/20210504160151.png"></p><p>把原图删掉后将画布调整为生成图大小（例如我这就是210*210）</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/thun888/tuku@master/img/da21desf4s568gre46g.png"></p><p>选择 文件—导出（保存为.svg)</p><p><img src="C:\Users\22383\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20210504160641441.png" alt="image-20210504160641441"></p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/thun888/tuku@master/img/20210504161231.png" style="zoom:80%;" /><h5 id="后记"><a href="#后记" class="headerlink" title="后记"></a>后记</h5><p>要真想更好一点可以用这个为底，重绘一遍</p>]]></content>
    
    
