  <entry>
    <title>GitHub打不开的临时方法</title>
    <link href="https://thun888.xyz/2021/04/05/GitHub%E6%89%93%E4%B8%8D%E5%BC%80%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%B4%E6%97%B6%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95/"/>
    <id>https://thun888.xyz/2021/04/05/GitHub%E6%89%93%E4%B8%8D%E5%BC%80%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%B4%E6%97%B6%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95/</id>
    <published>2021-04-05T06:03:30.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-07-09T12:10:22.388Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h4 id="起因"><a href="#起因" class="headerlink" title="起因"></a>起因</h4><p>先看看github在国内的访问情况</p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/thun888/tuku@master/img/image-20210405140926865.png" alt="image-20210405140926865" style="zoom:80%;" /><p>挺好的，但我有时就死活打不开/加载不出来/慢（今年开始的，估计是墙加高了），过了几个小时又可以了，甚烦也</p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/thun888/tuku@master/img/image-20210405141149140.png" alt="image-20210405141149140" style="zoom:67%;" /><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/thun888/tuku@master/img/image-20210405141843803.png" alt="image-20210405141843803"></p><p>而平时开飞机也不会一直开着，用镜像源替换也很麻烦，故有此计</p><h4 id="How"><a href="#How" class="headerlink" title="How"></a>How</h4><p>因为我平时只是在Github查东西等不需要账号登录的操作，所以把发往github.com的请求全部重定向到hub.fastgit.org这个镜像源就ok了</p><p>先安装<a href="https://share.thun888.xyz/%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6/HeaderEditor.zip">Header Editor</a>下载解压安装到浏览器就好</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/thun888/tuku@master/img/image-20210405142037440.png" alt="image-20210405142037440"></p><p>点到上面的‘导出于导入’，再在‘下载规则’一栏中1填</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">https:&#x2F;&#x2F;share.thun888.xyz&#x2F;%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6&#x2F;github%E9%87%8D%E5%AE%9A%E5%90%91.json</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>点右边的下载箭头，再点下面的保存就好</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/thun888/tuku@master/img/image-20210405142528347.png" alt="image-20210405142528347"></p><h4 id="结果"><a href="#结果" class="headerlink" title="结果"></a>结果</h4><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/thun888/tuku@master/img/image-20210405142707436.png" alt="image-20210405142707436"></p><p>（当然，别用它来登账号）</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
