    <title>手把手做一个定时关机的脚本</title>
    <link href="https://thun888.xyz/2020/10/31/%E6%89%8B%E6%8A%8A%E6%89%8B%E5%81%9A%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%AE%9A%E6%97%B6%E5%85%B3%E6%9C%BA%E7%9A%84%E8%84%9A%E6%9C%AC/"/>
    <id>https://thun888.xyz/2020/10/31/%E6%89%8B%E6%8A%8A%E6%89%8B%E5%81%9A%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%AE%9A%E6%97%B6%E5%85%B3%E6%9C%BA%E7%9A%84%E8%84%9A%E6%9C%AC/</id>
    <published>2020-10-31T01:37:04.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-07-09T12:09:28.783Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="Shutdown"><a href="#Shutdown" class="headerlink" title="Shutdown"></a>Shutdown</h2><p>首先祭出主角</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Shutdown</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/thun888/tuku@master/img/20201031094718.png"></p><p>假设我们要在60秒后关机，只需输</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Shutdown -s -t 60</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>但这还不够，这样每次都要输一次指令，所以可以这样</p><h2 id="食用"><a href="#食用" class="headerlink" title="食用"></a>食用</h2><ul><li>再桌面右键—新建—文本文档</li></ul><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/thun888/tuku@master/img/image-20201031095122093.png" alt="image-20201031095122093"></p><p>名称随意</p><ul><li>打开这个新建的文本文档，复制以下内容</li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">@echo off</span><br><span class="line">set &#x2F;P time&#x3D;多少秒后关机 </span><br><span class="line">shutdown -s -t %time%</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>保存为.bat/.cmd后缀名(因为有中文所以还要把编码改为ANSI)</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/thun888/tuku@master/img/20201031095819.png"></p><p>运行效果</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/thun888/tuku@master/img/20201031100207.png"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/thun888/tuku@master/img/image-20201031100248613.png" alt="image-20201031100248613"></p><ul><li>但这还不够，都做到这个地步了，平时倒计时都是以分钟为单位，还输秒怎么能行？/滑稽</li></ul><p>再改一下</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">@echo off</span><br><span class="line">set &#x2F;P min&#x3D;多少分后关机 </span><br><span class="line">set &#x2F;a time &#x3D; %min%*60</span><br><span class="line">shutdown -s -t %time%</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>效果</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/thun888/tuku@master/img/20201031100717.png"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/thun888/tuku@master/img/20201031100735.png"></p><p>ps：可以用</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">shutdown -a</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>来取消</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
    <summary type="html">&lt;h2 id=&quot;Shutdown&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#Shutdown&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;Shutdown&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Shutdown&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;首先祭出主角&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight plain&quot;&gt;&lt;ta</summary>
      
    
    
    
    
